# CW Node Helper — Config + Doctor demo (works offline)
# Record: cd ~/dev/cw-node-helper && vhs assets/tapes/config.tape
Output assets/config.gif
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "SF Mono"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20

Type "cwhelper config" Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "cwhelper doctor" Enter
Sleep 3s
